        <strong>Calendar:</strong> 11th lunar day of the waning moon (dark fortnight / Krishna Paksha) in Pausha month (December/January)<br>
        <strong>Alternative Names:</strong> Pausha Krishna Ekadashi, Saphala Ekadashi<br>
        <strong>Meaning of name:</strong> "Saphala" refers to success or make all devotional activities successful (fruitful).<br>
